ub.io/stagecraft/ontology/dynamis/DamageType> . <https://spectacular-voyage.github.io/test-inn-ambush/rules/dynamis/srd-5-2-1/weapons/damage-type/psychic> a <https://spectacular-voyage.github.io/stagecraft/ontology/dynamis/DamageType> . <https://spectacular-voyage.github.io/test-inn-ambush/rules/dynamis/srd-5-2-1/weapons/damage-type/radiant> a <https://spectacular-voyage.github.io/stagecraft/ontology/dynamis/DamageType> . <https://spectacular-voyage.github.io/test-inn-ambush/rules/dynamis/srd-5-2-1/weapons/damage-type/slashing> a <https://spectacular-voyage.github.io/stagecraft/ontology/dynamis/DamageType> . <https://spectacular-voyage.github.io/test-inn-ambush/rules/dynamis/srd-5-2-1/weapons/damage-type/thunder> a <https://spectacular-voyage.github.io/stagecraft/ontology/dynamis/DamageType> . }",
